{"tid":1440580,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"《FACEBOOK戰線》各區重要工作：Facebook18區群組輿論","createTime":"2019-08-10T12:58:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-18T00:02:52.000Z","uid":217816,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"1d10504b500cca91e118f2b769e584bf37679e20","tid":1440580,"uid":217816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T12:58:48.000Z","msg":"近來我係Facebook有時會見到啲on9藍絲post、假新聞，心諗我facebook應該無on9朋友會share，望真啲，原來係<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">馬鞍山之友</span></span></strong>啲人出既，於是我入去望，發現全個group充斥住班藍絲啲假新聞同on9言論，仲勁過老豆老母whatsapp group收果啲，<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">問題係係幾乎清一色係藍絲post，藍絲圍威喂係comment度鬧，帶曬風向，幾乎無我地手足出過post，或者反駁</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/54OiqEN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F54OiqEN.png&h=1861e9ab&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/suJY96t.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsuJY96t.png&h=2186d63f&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x4k8NS9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx4k8NS9.png&h=ac92f6a5&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8h9Q1da.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8h9Q1da.png&h=4e13788d&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xmUQ1db.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxmUQ1db.png&h=b1521a05&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/s4bTeyd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs4bTeyd.png&h=4a8ce52b&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n可以想像啲無腦既人、唔知發生咩事既人睇完佢地<span style=\"color: red;\">每日洗版式post 假新聞，對我地爭取中間派支持係幾咁不利</span><br />\n<br />\n所以！我地唔好再沉醉係同温層度，airdrop會收野既人可能好多都係手足以示支持，我地要再主動出擊，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">佢地玩輿論出網軍，我地都要玩，因為網軍影響力真係好撚大，文宣工作要入埋各區區群組！！</span><br />\n<br />\n自己果區自己救！！"},{"pid":"f17119907185e40769fc48e782a8efb48d49a0a1","tid":1440580,"uid":217816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T13:03:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5ccb3d96455bc524e0e7d357e49b4547f1e05c11","tid":1440580,"uid":217816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T13:03:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6848df522bc5db39c9db89b96c14b28b3bf9b424","tid":1440580,"uid":217816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T13:04:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b9276740263b7f9831738fde628b6a7aa1d88412","tid":1440580,"uid":217816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T13:04:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4a97c7bb672d261a54f84272819b866df6492279","tid":1440580,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T13:12:20.000Z","msg":"Push<br />\n建立社區"},{"pid":"cb7d9ea167bf64723b29f9474e49b352ed75d1fb","tid":1440580,"uid":32473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T13:17:41.000Z","msg":"全港18區既d18 fb page都係共狗開既"},{"pid":"e00c798fa8a77a95f67d262665ff18c1e9842af0","tid":1440580,"uid":217816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T13:18:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f010a68f8b12308beec51c272b8501f9415dcb11","tid":1440580,"uid":217816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T13:18:27.000Z","msg":"《FACEBOOK戰線》各區重要工作：Facebook18區群組輿論<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1440580\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1440580</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c962aa5d8a4c936f9413ee99f1a169aa0ad1af2d","tid":1440580,"uid":32473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T13:18:40.000Z","msg":"如果要打網戰最直接諗到各區巴打入返去自己果區個藍絲page做文宣"},{"pid":"a5d164c9b0c3e30ef480796dc9c945dd5f4104cc","tid":1440580,"uid":291996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T13:19:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dad6e197277ec054218c98d8ec7e7b3c9185b5c0","tid":1440580,"uid":291996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T13:19:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"26ab187dd4703fa0afbe98ccec50156f2d20fcb3","tid":1440580,"uid":217816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T13:23:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"702a515163d5b233e8e168a6b936bad696241fb8","tid":1440580,"uid":217816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T13:24:18.000Z","msg":"屌佢老母推"},{"pid":"4e34f957df993737dc4e819b8ec5323edb7b2e0d","tid":1440580,"uid":269171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T13:30:52.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c8ff615f05b419676f7df14b6f9a2f48a2b1c9f","tid":1440580,"uid":217816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T14:53:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5b8d460b00cdf62d15754683f46c073cec0797c0","tid":1440580,"uid":217816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T15:04:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"433e38c00711f444cfb8a4b1505bf25444d0e6cc","tid":1440580,"uid":80592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T15:25:13.000Z","msg":"<pre><code data-type=\"\">雖然抗爭時間久了，但絕對不能忘記，\n我們一直以來的理念，一定要堅持下去。</code></pre><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><br />\n<br />\n推爆文宣行動post<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n做事手法好重要<br />\n對家文宣強咗 文宣要大大力做<br />\n記者會都係文宣嘅一種<br />\n對內：AirDrop同路人 行動 戰略 方向<br />\n對外：Facebook扮中立拉攏藍絲 放分化藍絲嘅文宣 WhatsApp forward都係重要嘅渠道<br />\n國際：機場派外文文宣 播英文片 最新派埋文宣USB<br />\n</div></span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DrLgUUu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thum